  <p>Our instructors range in playing strength and experience from intermediate tournament level all the way up to International Grandmaster. Most have participated in provincial and national championships and beyond. Some have professional experience producing training materials, editing chess magazines, and coaching at the provincial and national level.</p>
  <p>Instructors are assigned to classes based on availability and experience level. All instructors have contributed to the creation of course materials and continually work towards further improving how we deliver our teaching curriculum.</p>

