      <p>Aman was the coach of Team Canada at the World Youth Championships from 2013 to 2015, including coaching Qiyu Zhou to a gold medal in the G14 category in 2014. Aman was also the coach of the Canadian Women's Olympiad team in 2016 and has experience instructing chess camps and teaching privately for over a decade.</p>
